<div class="mt-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-inset px-3 py-2.5">
  <% if mint %>
    <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted">Escrow mint: <span class="font-mono text-ink-secondary"><%= host %></span></p>
  <% end %>
  <p class="<%= "mt-1 " if mint %>text-xs leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
    A Cashu mint custodies the backing sats. If it goes offline or fails, locked funds can be lost even though
    the lock is yours, and the timelock refund needs the mint online to pay out. Fund only what you can afford to lose.
  </p>
</div>
